title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 26 2021

description:
Lara Logan's passionate plea for America to rise up against tyranny. There is no deadline in Afghanistan, America can still do what's right, Biden should stop pretending the Taliban makes the rules. America may never recover from this embarrassment in the eyes of the world. Death toll mounts as more American service members confirmed dead, Biden remains silent. Biden is already one of the worst presidents in history.
